BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-marin-brat-pack/
UID:event_313919427@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260401T031104Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260412T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260412T130000
SUMMARY:French Market Marin
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\n**Join us at a French Style Antique Ma
 rket in San Rafael**\n\n​Experience the ambiance of the French markets i
 n Paris right here in Marin.\nThe market brings together over 140 booths o
 f vintage and antique treasures.\nEnjoy a Sunday stroll through aisles of 
 home and garden décor\, vintage and estate jewelry\, collectibles\, books
 \, vintage shabby chic\, farmhouse style\, art\, pottery\, silver rugs and
  a host of other items. Listen to live French music\, grab a tasty crepe\,
  greet your favorite exhibitor with "Bonjour" and come home with a treasur
 e or two.\n\nMore info:\nwww.thefrenchmarketmarin.com
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-marin-brat-pack/events/3139194
 27/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260323T235143Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260323T235143Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
